 |last5=Duncan |first5=J.
 |title=The Calibration of the Hubble Space Telescope Kuiper Belt Object Search: Setting the Record Straight
 |journal=[[Astrophysical_Journal_Letters|Astrophysical Journal Letters]]
 |volume=503 |issue=1 |page=L89
 |year=1998
 |doi=10.1086/311515
}}</ref>，但這些檢測結果仍受到質疑<ref name="Brown1997">
{{cite journal
